object.customQuery:
SELECT PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Policy_Key,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Policy_Key_Code,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Major_Peril_ID,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Risk_State_ID,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Account_Entered_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Inforce_Premium,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Stateline,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.annual_statement_line,
TGT.row_id,
TGT.md5_hash_value
FROM
 dbo.PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums
 left join dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw2 TGT on
	PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Policy_Key = TGT.Policy_Key AND
	PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Policy_Key_Code = TGT.Policy_Key_Code AND
	PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Major_Peril_ID = TGT.Major_Peril_ID AND
	PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Risk_State_ID = TGT.Risk_State_ID AND
	PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Account_Entered_Dt = TGT.Account_Entered_Dt AND
	NVL(PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.StateLine,'NA') = NVL(TGT.StateLine,'NA') AND
	NVL(PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.annual_statement_line,'NA') = NVL(TGT.annual_statement_line,'NA')
WHERE
--Account_Entered_Dt >=dateadd(month, -1, cast(getdate() as date)) AND
date_part(year,PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.account_entered_dt) in ('2024') AND
--2006 and 2007 and '2008','2009','2010','2011' and '2012','2013','2014','2015' and '2016','2017','2018','2019' initial load was done in subsets of years
row_ins_dt >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views')
--PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Account_Entered_Dt >= convert(datetime,'1/1/2012',101)
--year(Account_Entered_Dt) = 2023
ORDER BY PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Policy_Key,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Policy_Key_Code,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Major_Peril_ID,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Risk_State_ID,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Account_Entered_Dt,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.Stateline,
PMS_Fact_Inforce_Premiums.annual_statement_line,
TGT.row_id,
TGT.md5_hash_value

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

transformations.description: This is a helper expression for EXPTRANS, used to resolve the name conflicts.
transformations.name: _EXPR_EXPTRANS

fields.name: in_MD5_Hash
fields.expression:
md5(policy_key||
policy_key_code||
major_peril_id||
risk_state_id||
account_entered_dt||
o_Inforce_Policy_key||
o_Inforce_Premium||
o_row_count||
annual_statement_line||
stateline)

fields.name: Flag
fields.expression: IIF(ISNULL(row_id),'I',IIF(NOT ISNULL(row_id) AND (in_MD5_Hash<>md5_hash_value),'U',IIF(NOT ISNULL(row_id) AND ISNULL(md5_hash_value),'U','R')))
